Eitodolua Esekiel emanata napuoi aamuat Yerusalem


1  “Ore iyie, Nakerai e tung'ani, iwa osoit nirragie te dukuya iyie, nisir ilkererin te ilo soit oitodolu enkanasa e Yerusalem; 
2  nipik emanata amuat Yerusalem, nishetu esuntai aitaman, nituru olong'elu aitaman ninye, intasheyie sii ilng'oborri te mbata, niun ilkedeta aitaman ninye. 
3  Niya esaani e sekenkei nipik ninye aitaa esuntai e sekenkei te rishata ino o enkanasa; nintorioki enkomom ino ninye, nincho metaa enatii ewueji osempewuet, nirrumoki osempewuet ninye. Keaku ena olmonekie le nkaji e Israel.


4  “Nirrag iyie te nkalo ino e kedienye, naa kairragie enkitamioto enkaji e Israel te shumata ino; amu ore esiana oo nkolong'i nirrag apetaa, naa inapaki ninche enkitamioto enye. 
5  Amu kaaisho nanu iyie nkolong'i esiana oo nkolong'i iip uni o ntomoni naaudo, naarisiore esiana oo larin lenkitamioto enye; metaa erishata naba neijia imbung ina kitamioto enkaji e Israel. 
6  Ore peyie indip ena, nintoki airrag eniare, kake ore te nkalo ino e tatene, ninap enkitamioto enkaji e Yuda; inkolong'i artam aatipika ena, enkolong ake to lari pooki.


7  “Naa intorioki enkomom ino ina manata namuati Yerusalem, metii toki enkaina ino; nimbonoki ina anasa. 
8  Naa ng'ura, ekaapik iyie inkeenta, metaa mimbelekenyakino ae alo, ometaba anaa niishu nkolong'i inono nimanie ina anasa.


9  “Ore iyie, iwa enkano o shairi, mpoosho o lpompo, o loikempe, o enkurma napuyiapui nipik nena pooki eng'irra nabo, nintobiru emukate te ninche. Ore te siadi e nena olong'i nirrag te murte ino; inkolong'i iip uni o ntomoni naaudo ina mukate. 
10  Naa ore endaa ninya naa keineneng'i, inchekelini tikitam te nkolong; ninya enkata nabo te nkolong. 
11  Neaku iok enkare te ntemata ematua e ile e hini; niok kata nabo te nkolong. 
12  Naa inya ninye anaa emukate e shairi, naa ipeju ninye te nkima nainokieki nkik oo ltung'ana edolita pooki ng'ae.”


13  Nejo Olaitoriani, “Neija eiko iltung'ana loo Siraeli tenenya emukate enye eeta oloirerio, tiatua iloreren laitarasaki ninche.”


14  Ina peyie ajo, “Aha, Olaitoriani Enkai! eitu aekata aisarkionie kewan; ina kata eton ara olbarnoti o matubulu taata eitu aekata anya entoki natua openy arashu enataara ing'uesi e ntim, arashu etijing'a enkutuk ai endaa torrono.”


15  Ina peyie aajoki ninye nanu, “Ing'ura ekaaisho iyie ilboro le modiei e nkiteng te rishata oonkik o ltung'ani, neaku ninye ipejunye emukate ino.”


16  Aanyaaka ake sii ajoki, “Enkerai e tung'ani ing'ura ajo kadung'oo ine neimu emukate e Yerusalem; ee kenya ninche imukateni naaineneng'i te ntemet naineneng'ishoreki te nkuretisho; naa keok enkare naturuni tenking'ashing'ash sapuk. 
17  Ekaas ena peyie meitoki aatum emukate o enkare, neing'ura maate te nkidang'ata sapuk, neibiitiari tiatua enkitamioto enye.

